des:
The official Alexa skill for the ZEEQ by REM-Fit SmartPillow.

ZEEQ is the super comfy pillow that plays your music, monitors and reacts to your snoring, analyzes your sleep and intelligently wakes you up.

The ZEEQ Alexa skill is designed for use with the ZEEQ by REM-Fit SmartPillow. You are able to ask Alexa all of your pillow data easily with your voice. Ask about your SleepScore, Snore stats, Restful Sleep stats and more!

 

Use phrases like:

"Alexa Ask my ZEEQ for my SleepScore from last night"

"Alexa Ask my ZEEQ to tell me the thought of the day"

"Alexa Ask my ZEEQ for battery status"

"Alexa Ask my ZEEQ how much restful sleep I got"

"Alexa Ask my ZEEQ how healthy have I been eating this week"

Note: Alexa and Amazon, Inc. do not store or retain your ZEEQ data, but voice interactions associated with your Amazon Account may contain your ZEEQ data.
